                    <p>We're not just sellers; we're tech enthusiasts who understand the importance of finding the perfect device for your specific needs. Whether you're a creative professional, a hardcore gamer, or a business leader, we have solutions tailored just for you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
            
            <div class="values-container">
                <div class="value-card">
