                    <p>We never compromise on quality. Every product in our catalog meets rigorous standards for performance, durability, and value.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">♥</div>
                    <h3>Customer First</h3>
                    <p>Your satisfaction is our top priority. We're committed to providing exceptional service at every step of your shopping journey.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">↻</div>
                    <h3>Innovation</h3>
                    <p>We constantly evolve and adapt, bringing you the latest technologies and solutions as soon as they become available.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">⚖</div>
                    <h3>Integrity</h3>
                    <p>Honesty and transparency guide all our business practices. What you see is exactly what you get - no surprises.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="stats-section">
            <div class="stats-container">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>5K+</h3>
                    <p class="tagline">Happy Customers</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>50+</h3>
                    <p class="tagline">Products</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>99%</h3>
                    <p class="tagline">Satisfaction Rate</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>24/7</h3>
                    <p class="tagline">Customer Support</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="partners-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Partners</h2>
            <p class="partners-text">We've partnered with the world's leading technology brands to bring you premium products at competitive prices.</p>
            
            <div class="brand-names">
                <div class="brand-name">Apple</div>
                <div class="brand-name">Dell</div>
                <div class="brand-name">HP</div>
                <div class="brand-name">Lenovo</div>
                <div class="brand-name">Samsung</div>
                <div class="brand-name">Asus</div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="cta-section">
            <h2>Ready to Upgrade Your Tech?</h2>
            <p>Browse our collection of premium computers, laptops, and accessories today. Experience the Tech Verse difference – where quality meets innovation.</p>
            <button class="btn">Shop Now</button>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
